name: Crescent Moon Cookies
description:
We at Crescent Moon take great care in using the very best of ingredients when making our lovely treats - from the velvety smooth chocolate and sweet vanilla icing, to the moist cocoa, cake-like cookie. At first glance, you will doubt being able to finish one! After the first bite, you will wish you had more!

These dangerously delicious cookies are made fresh to order! You will receive TWELVE HUGE, 3" round cookies, individually wrapped and packed with care. 
Want to send it for a birthday, anniversary or Thank You gift???J Let us know! We will include a personalized greeting card from you and ship to the address of your choice!

name: Peanut Butter Jelly Time
description:
Ok, time to have a little fun! Who can go wrong with good ol' PB and J? A wonderful, chewy peanut buttery cookie delivers just a taste of your favorite fruity flavor! 

In this order, we will send to you not 12, but 18 LARGE cookies, with the fruit flavor of your choice. Our default flavor is Strawberry. so, if you do not specify, that is what we will send to you. (our favorite!) 

Other popular flavors have been Currant, blackberry, grape, apricot, cherry. You pick it!

We Ship on Wednesdays and Fridays.

A great cookie for summer cookouts - colorful, yet no melty bits!!

name: Cool Lime Cookies
description:
A refreshing cookie for summer, the lime and chocolate are a perfect balance for one another. The lime is subtle at first, but by the end of the first bite, your mouth will awaken with a citrus explosion. The rich sweetness of the white chocolate calms everything down for a lovely cookie munching experience!

This order will bring you 12 tangy treats! We ship on Wednesdays and Fridays, always priority.

name: Orangina Cookies
description:
We at Crescent Moon take great care in using the very best of ingredients when making our lovely treats - 

Summer is in the air! So is the smell of fresh oranges! Freshly squeezed orange juice helps to make these cookies fluffy and light. Topped with a delightful icing and a pinch of orange peel!


These dangerously delicious cookies are made fresh to order! You will receive TWELVE large Oranginas, individually wrapped and packed with care. 

Want to send it for a birthday, anniversary or Thank You gift???J Let us know! We will include a personalized greeting card from you and ship to the address of your choice!
